I think that as you get to know the virus, you will test the model.
ç›®å‰æˆ‘ä»¬æŒæ¡çš„æƒ…å†µï¼Œå¹¶ä¸æ˜¯è¿™ä½ç§‘å­¦å®¶è®¡ç®—çš„æ¨¡å‹æƒ…å†µã€‚
What we have now is not the model that the scientist has calculated.
